            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/andy_stern_209690",
        "quote": "It has no enforceable standards to stop a union from conspiring with employers to keep another stronger union out or from negotiating contracts with lower pay and standards that members of another union have spent a lifetime establishing.",
